<div id="my-carousel" class="carousel about-carousel slide mb-5" data-ride="carousel">
  <ol class="carousel-indicators">
    <li data-target="#my-carousel" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
    <li data-target="#my-carousel" data-slide-to="1"></li>
    <li data-target="#my-carousel" data-slide-to="2"></li>
  </ol>
  <div class="carousel-inner">
    <div class="carousel-item active">
      <%= image_tag 'beer1.jpg',style:"object-fit: cover; object-position: 50% 75%;", class:"bd-placeholder-img bd-placeholder-img-lg d-block w-100" %>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="carousel-caption">
          <h1 class="heading-1">BEER FOR MEMORY</h1>
          <p class="caption-1">
            お祝い事や宴会など，<br>
            幸せなひとときをビールと共に。<br>
            貴方の記憶に残る麦酒を。
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="carousel-item">
      <%= image_tag 'beer2.jpg',style:"object-fit: cover; object-position: 50% 63%;", class:"bd-placeholder-img bd-placeholder-img-lg d-block w-100"  %>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="carousel-caption">
          <h1 class="heading-3">BEER FOR ENERGY</h1>
          <p class="caption-3">
            ビールが喉を潤せば，<br>
            貴方に元気が湧いてくる。<br>
            麦酒は，貴方の明日を頑張る活力に。
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="carousel-item">
      <%= image_tag 'beer3.jpg',style:"object-fit: cover; object-position: 50% 50%;", class:"bd-placeholder-img bd-placeholder-img-lg d-block w-100"  %>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="carousel-caption">
          <h1 class="heading-2">BEER FOR RELAXING</h1>
          <p class="caption-2">
            「一日お疲れ様。」<br>
            頑張った自分を労うビール。<br>
            麦酒で貴方に安らぎの時間を。
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#my-carousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
      <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
    </a>
    <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#my-carousel" role="button" data-slide="next">
      <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</div>
